# Bundled binaries (downloaded out-of-band, not checked in)
#
# Drop the universal macOS Ollama binary here as `ollama` before building
# the .app bundle. The build picks it up via electron-builder's
# extraResources, lands it at `process.resourcesPath/bin/ollama`, and
# packages/app/main/bundled.ts resolves it from there at runtime.
#
# Download:
#   curl -L https://github.com/ollama/ollama/releases/latest/download/ollama-darwin -o ollama
#   chmod +x ollama
#
# This file exists only to keep the directory tracked in git. Do not check
# in the binary itself — large, signed artifacts belong out of band.
